component.illusobjdesc:
Adam and Eve kiss while seated on a bed of flowers.  Eve is nude and faces forward with her head turned up and to the right in profile as she looks at Adam.  Her hair is long and curly.  
                  She appears to lean against Adam with her right leg bent and her left leg extended down and to the left.  Her right arm is at her side and with her left she embraces or holds Adam; 
                  her left hand holds the back of Adam's head.

Eve stands among the roots of the Tree of Knowledge with her knees slightly bent.  Her legs are together; at least her right foot is on tiptoe.  She is nude with long hair.  Her right arm is bent and holds the body of a 
                  serpent around her hips.  She is bound by the snake, at least in part, and looks to its head.  Her left arm is bent upwards and she cradles the head of the serpent in her left hand.  She bends to the right at her waist towards the serpent and turns her head to the right.  Eve's mouth is open with upper teeth visible; 
                  she takes and eats the fruit directly from the serpent's mouth in an eroticized parody of her kiss with Adam in the fifth illustration.  Her hair is long and curly.
